Thanks [~subru].
I was testing this further by extending {{TestNoOverCommitPolicy}}  to include periodic reservations as well, as part of YARN-5330. 

I think we are missing:
{code}
      // remove periodic component
      netAvailable = RLESparseResourceAllocation.merge(resCalc,
              Resources.clone(totalCapacity), netAvailable, periodicRle,
              RLEOperator.subtractTestNonNegative, start, end);
{code}

As part of {{InMemoryPlan.getAvailableResourceOverTime(..)}}.  I will test this further.

